# ☕ Digital Connect Internet Café Management System

> A modern web-based Internet Café Management System developed to streamline customer registration, computer allocation, session management, billing, printing services, and administrative reporting.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

The **Digital Connect Internet Café Management System** is a comprehensive web application designed to automate the daily operations of an internet café. The system replaces manual record-keeping with an efficient digital platform, improving productivity, reducing errors, and enhancing customer service.

This project was developed as part of the **Bachelor of Information Technology in Business Systems** qualification and demonstrates practical application of software engineering principles, database management, and web development technologies.

---

# 🎯 Objectives

The main objectives of this project are to:

* Automate customer registration.
* Manage computer availability.
* Monitor internet sessions.
* Generate customer bills.
* Manage printing services.
* Produce administrative reports.
* Improve operational efficiency.
* Reduce manual paperwork.
* Provide secure user authentication.

