# ⚙️ Installation

## Requirements

* PHP 8+
* MySQL
* XAMPP or WAMP
* Modern Web Browser

## Installation Steps

1. Clone the repository.

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Digital-Connect-Internet-Cafe-Management-System.git
```

2. Copy the project folder into the XAMPP `htdocs` directory.

3. Start:

* Apache
* MySQL

4. Open phpMyAdmin.

5. Create a new database.

6. Import the SQL database file.

7. Open your browser and visit:

```text
http://localhost/Digital-Connect-Internet-Cafe-Management-System
```

